GET http://localhost:1234/mapInPlay/0/ressetMithReserve


### Crear un nuevo mapa in Play
POST http://localhost:1234/mapInPlay
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "idMap": 1,
    "IDUserHost": "user_2x7hdgi9dwczRgUdQy93PLpgrUq"
}

